#### Requirements

1. An online store with WordPress and WooCommerce infrastructure. This plugin need minimum requirement WordPress Version 3.9.1 and WooCommerce Version 2.1.11.
2. Plugin already test with Wordpress v4.5 and Woocommerce v2.5
3. PHP minimum version 5.4.
4. Midtrans plugin for WooCommerce \[ [Github](https://github.com/veritrans/veritrans-woocommerce) \| [Zip](https://github.com/veritrans/veritrans-woocommerce/archive/master.zip) \].

