#### Installation Process

1. Extract .zip file that you have previously downloaded.
2. Upload the .zip extraction folder into WordPress installation directory `wp-content/plugins/`
3. Activate Midtrans plugin from Plugin menu in your WordPress admin page.
<br />

#### Plugin Configuration

In order to configure Midtrans-WooCommerce plug-in:

1. Access your WordPress admin page.
2. Go to **WooCommerce - Settings - Checkout** menu in the WordPress admin page.
3. In Payment Gateway option, pick Veritrans then click **settings**.
4. Insert required fields following the figure below.
<br /><br />
    ![WooCommerce Setting](/images/woocomm00.png){: .img-responsive .img-thumbnail}
<br /><br />

5. Login to MAP portal to configure a few options below:

    | URL Role | Redirect URL|
    |---|---|
    | Payment Notification URL | http://[your web]/?wc-api=WC_Gateway_Veritrans |
    | Finish Redirect URL | http://[your web]/?wc-api=WC_Gateway_Veritrans |
    | Error Redirect URL | http://[your web]/?wc-api=WC_Gateway_Veritrans |
    | Unfinish Redirect URL | http://[your web]/?wc-api=WC_Gateway_Veritrans |

